biospec_descr.textblock:
1. Lipidogram, glycemia;

        2. Hormonal analyses by radioimmunoassay method ׃ total testosterone (T), free
           testosterone (FT), sex hormone binding globulin (SHBG), dehidroepiandrosterone sulphate
           (DHEAs), thyrotropin hormone (TSH), free thyroxine (FT4);

        3. Blood coagulation test׃ clotting time according to Ovren, fibrinogen, aPTT.

        4. Total blood picture test;

        5. Androgen  receptor (AR) polymorphism test.
